name: MoonBeans
description: Moonbeans is a dividend rewards token and the largest NFT marketplace on Moonriver, with new content being added every day! Thanks to Moonriver, a parachain powered by Kusama and part of the Moonbeam ecosystem, additional features such as profit sharing, full DAO integration and cross-chain interoperability are also available. Since launch, over $750,000 in dividend rewards have been distributed to $BEANS holders. The team has also established partnerships with all major projects and exchanges on Moonriver and other networks, including farming incentives, advertising campaigns, new NFT listings, community events and much more! "Be-an" innovator and join the Moonbeans community today to learn more!
